descriptionHtml:
VPN Australia - free and fast VPN app. Helps get Australian IP or unblock sites.


Get a Australian IP address with single-click ease via fast and free Vpn Australia service or use it for unlocking access to blocked websites and apps. OpenVPN connection technology featuring a 1024-bit key generated with OpenSSL provides a secure and confidential connection to open Wi-Fi networks.

You'll need a VPN in the following instances:
1. Changing your IP address to the VPN server's IP address.
2. Visiting websites and launching apps blocked by your Internet Service Provider.
3. Willing to conceal from your Internet Service Provider a fact of visiting certain websites. VPN provides anonymous access to websites and apps - your Internet Service Provider is only notified of you being connected to a VPN - all the web-traffic is encrypted with a 1024-bit key.
5. Connecting to open Wi-Fi networks (password-less). All the data in these networks is transmitted in the clear (without encryption). If a website doesn't feature an SSL, then all the information that you submit on this website may be intercepted by ill-intentioned persons. VPN encrypts traffic and prevents it from being read even in case of open Wi-Fi networks.

VPN Australia Features.

# Free, Unlimited and Multifunctional.
+ 100% free VPN service, forever.
+ VPN without registration.
+ No traffic limits.
+ Compatibility with any connections type.

# Blocked Content Unlocking
+ Bypassing lockdowns introduced by your Internet Service Provider.
+ Bypassing regional restrictions introduced by firewalls at school, offices, etc.
+ Getting access to the following blocked websites.
+ Unlocking VoIP networks and video calls.
+ Bypassing firewall at school.
+ Unlocking torrent.

# Protecting Your Privacy
+ Provides anonymous access to websites and apps.
+ Can be used for torrent downloading.
+ Changes IP address.
+ Doesn’t keep a log or save any info about you.

# Intuitive Controls and Convenience
+ For your convenience, we introduced two separate connection buttons. The first connects to a selected VPN in the list. The second connects directly to a Australian VPN. It's that simple. In case you need to change IP address, just select a server in some other country and establish a connection. In case you need to get a Australian IP address, just connect to a Australian VPN server in one click.
+ Easy to control, one click connection.
+ Searches the nearest server for maximum speed.
+ Searches a server with minimum neighbors.
+ Constantly growing pool of servers around the globe.

Our Servers.
Since there's no Internet censorship in Australia, Finland, Netherlands, Germany, France, Luxembourg and the US, connecting to one of these VPN servers opens access to the majority of websites;

VPN Servers PRO.
Reliable servers with minimum clients: currently, less than three clients are connected to our servers. We monitor servers and, in case client number exceeds ten, we activate an extra server.

Free VPN Servers.
Free services always enjoy huge popularity, and our servers are no different. As a rule, free servers' audience is 10-to-30 times larger than in case of PRO servers. If this number increases, we add an extra server. These servers operate smoothly, but sometimes a free server becomes overloaded - in this case you need to connect to some other free server or try PRO for 7 days for free.

If a PRO server in a specific country is required, please inform us by sending an email at altcoinapps@gmail.com.

VPN Australia makes it possible to get an Australian IP address or the IP of any other country from a standard list of servers in one click.

A secure connection is provided by OpenVPN technology with an OpenSSL key of 2048 bits. The Shadowsocks technology provides the fast one.

VPN Australia features

Application accessibility:
- Free and permanent.
- You do not need to register an account to use the VPN.
- No traffic limitation.
- It adapts to any type of connection.

Shows blocked content:
- Opens access to content that is only available in Australia.
- Blacklisted resources by the provider are accessible once you connect.
- Allows unrestricted use of blocked social networks, messengers, torrents (in PRO version).

User-friendly functionality:
- For your convenience, two separate connection buttons have been added. The first one allows you to connect to the selected VPN in the list. The second one automatically connects to the least loaded Australian VPN without searching through the list.
- Connection is performed in one click.
- To ensure maximum speed and connectivity, the AP searches for the nearest available server.
- Priority connection occurs to the server with the minimum number of neighbors.

VPN can be helpful in the following cases:
- It is necessary to open access to the content that is available only in a specific country.
- You need to change the current IP to the IP of the VPN server.
- Open Internet resources and applications blocked by your ISP.
- You connect to the websites, the information about which you don't want to pass to your provider. In this case, the VPN program guarantees the client an anonymous connection since the provider sees only the connection to the VPN operation. In this case, the traffic is encrypted with a key.
- Uses commonly available WIFI.

VPN application servers
The largest number of servers are in Australia, but the app also has servers in all the world's major locations, e.g., Germany, France, England, the United States, and Singapore. The PRO version includes all key countries plus more exotic locations, such as Malaysia, Turkey, South Africa, Brazil, Spain, etc.

PRO version
Stable servers with a minimum number of clients, usually not more than 3 - 5, are connected to the servers. We monitor the servers, and if there are more than ten clients, we will activate a new server.

Free version
With ads. It makes sense that most users prefer free servers. According to statistics, free VPN servers are used by 10 - 30 times more customers. If this number increases, we add a new server. The free servers are excellent for use, but sometimes one of the servers is overloaded. If so, you need to connect to another one or try the PRO version for 7 days for free.

In case of failures of a particular server, you should not leave 1 star. The best option would be to find another server or contact support: support@tap2free.net.

We are ready to add new locations, you can write to us at support@tap2free.net if you need a PRO server in a specific country.

creator: AltApps
descriptionHtml:
VPN Australia makes it possible to get an Australian IP address or the IP of any other country from a standard list of servers in one click.

A secure connection is provided by OpenVPN technology with an OpenSSL key of 2048 bits. The Shadowsocks technology provides the fast one.

VPN Australia features

Application accessibility:
- Free and permanent.
- You do not need to register an account to use the VPN.
- No traffic limitation.
- It adapts to any type of connection.

Shows blocked content:
- Opens access to content that is only available in Australia.
- Blacklisted resources by the provider are accessible once you connect.
- Allows unrestricted use of blocked social networks, messengers, torrents (in PRO version).

User-friendly functionality:
- For your convenience, two separate connection buttons have been added. The first one allows you to connect to the selected VPN in the list. The second one automatically connects to the least loaded Australian VPN without searching through the list.
- Connection is performed in one click.
- To ensure maximum speed and connectivity, the AP searches for the nearest available server.
- Priority connection occurs to the server with the minimum number of neighbors.

VPN can be helpful in the following cases:
- It is necessary to open access to the content that is available only in a specific country.
- You need to change the current IP to the IP of the VPN server.
- Open Internet resources and applications blocked by your ISP.
- You connect to the websites, the information about which you don't want to pass to your provider. In this case, the VPN program guarantees the client an anonymous connection since the provider sees only the connection to the VPN operation. In this case, the traffic is encrypted with a key.
- Uses commonly available WIFI.

VPN application servers
The largest number of servers are in Australia, but the app also has servers in all the world's major locations, e.g., Germany, France, England, the United States, and Singapore. The PRO version includes all key countries plus more exotic locations, such as Malaysia, Turkey, South Africa, Brazil, Spain, etc.

PRO version
Stable servers with a minimum number of clients, usually not more than 3 - 5, are connected to the servers. We monitor the servers, and if there are more than ten clients, we will activate a new server.

Free version
With ads. It makes sense that most users prefer free servers. According to statistics, free VPN servers are used by 10 - 30 times more customers. If this number increases, we add a new server. The free servers are excellent for use, but sometimes one of the servers is overloaded. If so, you need to connect to another one or try the PRO version for 7 days for free.

In case of failures of a particular server, you should not leave 1 star. The best option would be to find another server or contact support: support@tap2free.net.

We are ready to add new locations, you can write to us at support@tap2free.net if you need a PRO server in a specific country.
